details.name: Starstorm
details.description: Calls down a wave of meteors to damage nearby enemy units. The closest enemy unit to Mirana in a 425 radius will be struck a second time for 75% of the damage. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Passively triggers Starstorm every 10 seconds. Does not trigger if the enemy doesn't see Mirana.
